    <title>Understanding the Structure of the Universe</title>
    <parts>
        <part type="frq" must_not_have_multiple_instances="true">
            <main_text>
                <p>
                    <s>What is a galaxy?</s>
                </p>
            </main_text>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    <s>A galaxy is a collection of billions of stars.</s>
                </p>
            </answer>
            <solutions> 
                <solution>
                    <p>
                        <s>Earth and the other planets in the solar system orbit the Sun, which is a star.</s> 
                        <s>The Sun and lots of other stars together form a large group of stars which form a spiral pattern.</s> 
                        <s>This large group of stars is called a galaxy.</s> 
                        <s>Our galaxy is called the Milky Way, and there are billions of galaxies in the universe.</s>
                        <s>Each galaxy contains billions of stars.</s>
                        <s>So we can write 'A galaxy is a collection of billions of stars.'</s>
                    </p>
                </solution>
            </solutions>
